{"tid":1461734,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"而家個個剩係識捉鬼","createTime":"2019-08-13T09:07:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T10:10:40.000Z","uid":111934,"like":20,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"4e8998ecb6a4525c6aa9ebd509c58dbc43da377f","tid":1461734,"uid":111934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:07:28.000Z","msg":"醒啦<br />\n之前又話核彈都唔割<br />\n而家日日喺度搵「證據」想將所有嘢賴哂落黑警度<br />\n有啲擺明夾硬嚟, 仲要特登放大頭, 如果嗰個真係唔係黑警而係義士<br />\n比你地咁樣放大頭相真係多得你唔少<br />\n<br />\n成個運動又倒退返去2014年衝就係鬼, 升級就係鬼<br />\n如果唔係有升級送中一早過咗啦, 仲點會逼到港共狗急跳牆搵老黑幫拖, 比市民睇到警黑合作<br />\n<br />\n而家日日將所有升級行為賴哂落黑警度, 只係另類割蓆咋<br />\n日後勇武只會綁手綁腳, 怕比人話鬼<br />\n而無哂任何升級行為, 最開心就係港共, 黑警, 左膠咋"},{"pid":"ca50849fd5f26c76e893da4a6e30e5d10513d65f","tid":1461734,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:13:50.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"499f1b6484a8726b363ee641ab29123a6be4efb8","tid":1461734,"uid":4875,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:14:57.000Z","msg":"班人仲要覺得好撚風趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f99b6702d746ec817a60cb20369ffaa051f03470","tid":1461734,"uid":230890,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:15:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"568e0d596c4be275f7bd57652a5eb14d2c4743e5","tid":1461734,"uid":72510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:16:02.000Z","msg":"[置頂] [上線啦!!!] 夢遊機場 Online攻略<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dDeeNS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dDeeNS</a>"},{"pid":"f14cffe42728824c019459bb40e2060108245de6","tid":1461734,"uid":230890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:16:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2cc92ad6f0f137bff493cd57784dafd98e2d2d28","tid":1461734,"uid":230890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:16:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ccdd72e31f45f4d495f860e6d50a97c871655f00","tid":1461734,"uid"