/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e283b3166b97110371e53d0bdd9ab3c32fd3375","tid":1461734,"uid":59297,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:19:37.000Z","msg":"咪就係<br />\n<br />\n有冇咁鐘意捉鬼，咁得閒諗咁多捉鬼，不如諗下有咩計call馬、做好啲好過"},{"pid":"729435b37e1563d8abedc2c877ae5a939b0a5006","tid":1461734,"uid":264811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:20:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a92b8b8d0b53e267208ee1905b2d8cc4460460eb","tid":1461734,"uid":42367,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:21:18.000Z","msg":"鬼捉唔哂<br />\n<br />\n都唔需要特別去捉<br />\n<br />\n唔好比人帶風向"},{"pid":"b7e75716f071f3b5a2b118c46541fec6924f827e","tid":1461734,"uid":111934,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:25:31.000Z","msg":"逆向思考<br />\n就算黑警真係有臥底混入扮升級<br />\n點解佢地要咁做<br />\n<br />\n正正就係因為佢地好怕我地會升級行動呀<br />\n於是就用賤招引我地捉鬼<br />\n等我地互相猜忌, 唔敢再升級<br />\n佢地就可以減少壓力, 減少清場阻力<br />\n<br />\n不過最後都要提大家<br />\n升唔升級都好, 而家出去前線風險係大咗好多好多<br />\n各位自己都要小心衡量個人能力, 以不被捕為大前提"},{"pid":"912ae56fb8ec2f96e50cb9d36e202d17bf19b19a","tid":1461734,"uid":130797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:10:40.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n鬼既目的<br />\n就係要故意做成混亂<br />\n令我地咩都做唔到呀"}]}